body.description: Mount Your Dash Cam the Best Way Your dash cam is lacking something and that is our dash cam mirror mount, a must have dash cam accessory. Why you need it? Installing your dash cam in the position of the rear view mirror is an ideal location and will not block your view. reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A bit long but useful!
reviews.reviewText: The phone holder provides the capability of hanging my mobile phone under the rear view mirror instead of fixing an adhesive type holder. Adhesive type holders restrict the mag safe capability if I am using a magnetic type base. So I switched to this hanging type. It is quite sturdy, and I was able to hang it with its attachment easily. The only thing I have to contend with is blocking front view with my phone, which is in addition to my dash cam, which is affixed up at a higher elevation on the wind shield. I just have to get used to it.
